name: Social Icons Set
description:
Currently features 120 icons with 3 variants each!


This was based on Rounak Bose's Figma file for use in my project LinkPort.dev


I really liked his set but felt like it could make use of component variants and more. I'll post any changes below:


Added:

  • SoundCloud
  • TikTok


Removed:

  • Cloud
  • Google +
  • Heart
  • Kaixin001
  • Star
  • Mail_ru


Updated:

  • Discord
  • Dropbox
  • Dribbble
  • Facebook
  • Figma
  • Google
  • Linkedin
  • Mail
  • Reddit
  • Snapchat
  • Steam
  • Tumblr
  • Twitter


Other:

  • Small quality improvements
  • Reduced components into variants
  • Renaming / layer organization


Let me know what you think!
